    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You take in a deep breath and pull chakra from the environment, generating an aura of chakra around you of your chakra color. You may spend a number of Chakra Die up to half your level. For each chakra die spent, roll 2 Adaptability Die (this does not spend any). You gain the result of all die rolled + 1 for each Adaptability Die rolled, as chakra. If regaining chakra this way goes beyond your maximum, the difference becomes temporary chakra.</p>",
